{"tid":1630130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幾時先識唔再集中一區比人拉？","createTime":"2019-10-06T11:31:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:21:03.000Z","uid":16981,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1783e6e9178d767219e5da56d8f8b21283cc4620","tid":1630130,"uid":16981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:31:52.000Z","msg":"講撚咗遍地開花<br />\n次撚次都要攪大遊行<br />\n幾百萬人上街影張相之後比人大圍捕你哋開心啲？<br />\n<br />\n遍地開花<br />\n可以分散警力<br />\n又唔會冇車搭<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">被拉嘅人一定少過大遊行</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">受影響嘅地方愈大，對政府施嘅壓就愈大</span><br />\n<br />\n相反，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中只會比狗圍捕，而且成本愈高！</span></span><br />\n同埋200百萬人政府都唔理，你哋唔係諗住又封路又有黨鐵全線停駛嘅日子會有多過200萬人出到同一個地方？就算比你出到，你要啲手足點走？行返屋企？<br />\n<br />\n手足永遠都係我哋成場抗爭嘅最重要元素！<br />\n希望大家可以認真咁思考下呢一點<br />\n香港人，反抗！"},{"pid":"c2169f0a4cd416b36887025a3565833d867581f6","tid":1630130,"uid":2883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:33:51.000Z","msg":"尋日有班仆街係咁叫人去港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0673b623319902bd059bf56ce9c32afb6b44cd","tid":1630130,"uid":16981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:11:45.000Z","msg":"屌，巴士都比狗逗喇<br />\n仲集中出去一區遊行做乜撚嘢<br />\n仲有乜嘢陣地戰、對峙做乜鳩？<br />\n<br />\n遍地開花好地地，係要出去<br />\n睇住啲細路、小妹妹比人拉喇屌"},{"pid":"53b4eb1bc902ccd4b36575a1f2ac75b8968651cb","tid":1630130,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:12:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"a84e0b6953e1529bae3b3c8904e45691390c5c84","tid":1630130,"uid":235535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:13:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb1fa437b66f1bcbdc238b844968e7d1e994b38c","tid":1630130,"uid":16981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:21:03.000Z","msg":"不反對通知書都冇埋，仲想和平n百萬遊行？<br />\n人哋有黨鐵配合，又喺東隧set rb，又圍巴士<br />\n醒啲，唔好再比咁多機會啲狗捉啲手足啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}